    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blades For Hire Demo</strong> 为您打开了通往令人兴奋的佣兵公会管理和战术决策世界的大门。在这个无情的世界里，讲述一个平民为荣耀而奋斗的扣人心弦的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本演示中，您将体验到</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择的力量 完成独特的任务，你的决定将左右事态的发展。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战术战斗</strong>： 探索战斗机的间接控制系统。尝试各种策略，掌握关键的战斗机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180010/extras/168c8be07152f8e1f872584c2b1399d6.poster.avif?t=1754741253\" width=628 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180010/extras/168c8be07152f8e1f872584c2b1399d6.webm?t=1754741253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180010/extras/168c8be07152f8e1f872584c2b1399d6.mp4?t=1754741253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>雇佣兵管理</strong>： 招募坚强的战士，装备他们执行高风险任务，并将他们训练成精英战士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180010/extras/fb23b8ebb6e5e1020ffeb9052224367f.poster.avif?t=1754741253\" width=628 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180010/extras/fb23b8ebb6e5e1020ffeb9052224367f.webm?t=1754741253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经济规划</strong>： 明智地分配有限的资源、支付工资并投资于公会的发展，同时为佣兵生活中不可预测的开支做好准备。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该演示可让您一睹《Blades For Hire》的核心机制和氛围，让您体验艰难决策、战略规划的分量，以及等待完整游戏的紧张冒险。</p>",
